sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Attendant as Parking Attendant
participant ParkingConsole
participant ParkingService
participant ParkingRepository
participant ParkingJson as "parking.json"


Attendant->>ParkingConsole: Select "Search Vehicle"
ParkingConsole->>Attendant: Prompt for license plate
Attendant-->>ParkingConsole: plate
ParkingConsole->>ParkingService: searchVehicle(plate)
alt vehicle found
  ParkingService-->>ParkingConsole: slotId
  ParkingConsole-->>Attendant: Display slot assignment
else vehicle not found
  ParkingService-->>ParkingConsole: not found
  ParkingConsole-->>Attendant: Display error message
end
